MAKER Hub - Web3 Learning Platform

A decentralized learning platform where creators can publish courses and students earn certifications as NFT badges. Features include:

- Course creation and management
- Lesson editor with video, text, and code content
- Payment models: free, upfront escrow, and deferred payment
- Integration with smart contracts for escrow and rewards
- Creator dashboard and student learning portal

Built with Next.js, React, TypeScript, and Supabase.
